<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Confirm Your TrackerDelivery Account</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f4; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
    .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .logo { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #4f46e5); color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; color: #666; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">TrackerDelivery</div>
      <p>Restaurant Monitoring for Bali</p>
    </div>
    
    <h2>Welcome to TrackerDelivery!</h2>
    
    <p>Hi there,</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for signing up for TrackerDelivery! We're excited to help you monitor your restaurant's delivery platform status and prevent revenue losses.</p>
    
    <p>To get started, please confirm your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
    
    <div style="text-align: center;">
      <%= link_to "Confirm Your Email", @confirmation_url, class: "button" %>
    </div>
    
    <p>Or copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
    <p style="word-break: break-all; color: #2563eb;"><%= @confirmation_url %></p>
    
    <p><strong>This confirmation link will expire in 24 hours.</strong></p>
    
    <p>Once confirmed, you'll be able to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>🔔 Get instant alerts when your restaurant goes offline</li>
      <li>📊 Monitor GrabFood and GoFood status 24/7</li>
      <li>💰 Prevent revenue losses from unnoticed closures</li>
      <li>📱 Receive notifications via email and WhatsApp</li>
    </ul>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>If you didn't create a TrackerDelivery account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The TrackerDelivery Team</p>
      <p>Questions? Reply to this email or visit our help center.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>